== 三維雙曲空間的正扭歪無限面體 ==
1967年時，C. W. L. Garner以類似於在歐式[[三維空間|三維空間]]尋找正扭歪無限面體的方式，發現了31種雙曲空間中具有扭歪多邊形頂點圖的正扭歪無限面體<ref>Garner, C. W. L. ''Regular Skew Polyhedra in Hyperbolic Three-Space.'' Canad. J. Math. 19, 1179–1186, 1967. [http://cms.math.ca/cjm/a145822] {{Wayback|url=http://cms.math.ca/cjm/a145822 |date=20150402131943 }} Note: His paper says there are 32, but one is self-dual, leaving 31.</ref>。

